00:04:47.650 --> 00:04:52.480
Benito Juarez was from the state
of [inaudible] in the south,

00:04:52.480 --> 00:04:54.230
which is an indigenous state.

00:04:54.230 --> 00:04:58.320
He was Zapotec Indian both sides,

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:01.510
