himself to a lawyer,

00:05:27.470 --> 00:05:30.950
and he ultimately became a lawyer.

00:05:30.950 --> 00:05:34.420
The mythology says that he
married the lawyer's daughter,

00:05:34.420 --> 00:05:37.840
but that's under dispute
at the moment,

00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:43.200
but he certainly married Margarita,
and he went on from there.

00:05:43.200 --> 00:05:49.030
He became governor of
the state of Oaxaca,

00:05:49.030 --> 00:05:53.430
and he was an avowed opponent
of Antonio Lopez de Santa Anna

00:05:53.430 --> 00:05:54.810
who you probably have heard of.

00:05:54.810 --> 00:05:59.550
And Santa Anna exiled him.

00:05:59.550 --> 00:06:03.090
