00:06:22.510 --> 00:06:27.300
As soon as the revolution of
Ayutla in 1854 was declared,

00:06:27.300 --> 00:06:31.780
Juarez and a lot of other
Mexican exiles left the U.S.

00:06:31.780 --> 00:06:33.250
and went back to Mexico.

00:06:33.250 --> 00:06:38.730 position:56%
Santana resigned from the presidency
the following year in 1855

00:06:38.730 --> 00:06:43.650
and Juarez became the Minister
of Justice in the cabinet

00:06:43.650 --> 00:06:48.980
and he is responsible for
a law called the Le Juarez

00:06:48.980 --> 00:06:52.930
