00:17:07.260 --> 00:17:09.110
&gt;&gt; Barbara Tenenbaum: Well, I
would like to be able to say

00:17:09.110 --> 00:17:11.980
that this was the last
intervention into Mexico.

00:17:11.980 --> 00:17:18.200 position:56%
But unfortunately, the United States
intervened twice in the 20th century

00:17:18.200 --> 00:17:26.980
in Mexico, once to -- it's a
very confusing story that needs

00:17:26.980 --> 00:17:29.610
to be really written
more extensively.

00:17:29.610 --> 00:17:33.610
Once in [inaudible] where we were
there for probably almost a year

00:17:33.610 --> 00:17:35.000
and the other was when [inaudible].

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:42.040
