they were at the same time.

00:19:52.580 --> 00:19:57.770 position:56%
So you had Lincoln in the United
States and Juarez in Mexico and both

00:19:57.770 --> 00:19:59.620
of them saved the nationality

00:19:59.620 --> 00:20:03.050
of their respective republics,
and that was wonderful.

00:20:03.050 --> 00:20:08.120
