Latina, you should think about it

00:25:55.870 --> 00:26:01.110
because that -- Napoleon
said after all,

00:26:01.110 --> 00:26:06.070
the western hemisphere
is mostly Catholic

00:26:06.070 --> 00:26:10.650
and Romance language speaking so
therefore it's Latin American.

00:26:10.650 --> 00:26:15.540
The other thing is
really quite funny.

00:26:15.540 --> 00:26:21.130
