lot of dispute but there is a school

00:26:33.370 --> 00:26:37.580
of thought that says the
mariachi came from marriages

00:26:37.580 --> 00:26:41.620
that were performed
during the empire,

00:26:41.620 --> 00:26:45.110
and the French word
marriage became mariachi.

00:26:45.110 --> 00:26:48.350
So and that has stuck.

00:26:48.350 --> 00:26:51.900
